* Elvan Abeylegesse TUR disqualified from the competition for doping in accordance with International Association of Athletics Federations (IAAF)’s announcement of 29 March 2017 after retesting her samples from the 2007 World Championship. Results annulled from 25.08.07 to 25.08.09 and banned for 2 years.
